    <item>
      <title>感谢私募股权的寿司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/thank-private-equity-for-your-sushi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对寿司的需求在美国增长。彭博的Dani Burger参观了Baja Aqua Farms，这是Sashimi-Grade Tuna的顶级生产商之一，探讨了金枪鱼的耕种方式和太平洋蓝鳍金枪鱼的独特模型。我们与Equity Group Investments的Mark Sotir坐下来，了解私募股权在金枪鱼中看到的机会。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/thank-private-equity-for-your-sushi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 12:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>令人惊讶的输出徒步之后，沙特阿拉斯股价在亚洲几天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/saudis-slash-oil-prices-for-asia-days-after-surprise-output-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+联盟宣布出乎意料的大型输出飙升之后的几天，沙特阿拉伯在两年多以上的旗舰石油价格上涨了最多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/saudis-slash-oil-prices-for-asia-days-after-surprise-output-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 11:41:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾将卖空规则收紧到平静的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/taiwan-tightens-short-selling-rules-to-calm-market-amid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的金融监管机构宣布，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的积极关税中，稳定市场的销量更严格，以稳定市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/taiwan-tightens-short-selling-rules-to-calm-market-amid-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 11:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚向奈拉避免关税后果提供美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/nigeria-supplies-dollars-to-shield-naira-from-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚的中央银行将美元卖给了贷方，以阻止奈拉汇率的侵蚀，这是在美国关税动荡引起的抛售后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/nigeria-supplies-dollars-to-shield-naira-from-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 09:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度专注于贸易协议，避免对美国关税进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度一位印度政府官员说，印度不太可能立即对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税征收，并将努力集中在与美国达成双边贸易协定方面，以降落职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 09:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东股票，Aramco沉没在关税，石油的双重威胁上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/mideast-stocks-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-on-oil-tariff-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括沙特阿拉伯在内的中东国家的主要股票基准沉没在2020年以来，这是投资者对全球贸易战争和石油价格低迷的风险的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/mideast-stocks-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-on-oil-tariff-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 08:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港金融负责人表示，关税对全球贸易构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/hong-kong-financial-chief-says-tariffs-a-threat-to-global-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财政大臣保罗·陈（Paul Chan）在周日的博客文章中说，美国关税破坏了国际贸易，最终将伤害美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/hong-kong-financial-chief-says-tariffs-a-threat-to-global-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 06:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国公司可以从特朗普关税中获得竞争优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/uk-companies-could-gain-competitive-advantage-from-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家称，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对英国出口的优惠待遇使该国的公司具有竞争优势，可以保护经济免受华盛顿贸易战最糟糕的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/uk-companies-could-gain-competitive-advantage-from-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国投资者周一对美国关税报复的“丑陋”付出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-investors-brace-for-ugly-monday-on-us-tariff-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，中国投资者正在努力严峻，因为该国的市场从延长的周末返回，并将其报复给美国关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-investors-brace-for-ugly-monday-on-us-tariff-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 05:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通货膨胀将给出一些特朗普关税痛苦的暗示</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/trump-tariffs-us-inflation-is-set-to-give-hints-of-trade-levy-pain-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，美国家庭的总体通货膨胀率可能降低了，这是经济学家在唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税海啸之后，这一缓刑是暂时的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/trump-tariffs-us-inflation-is-set-to-give-hints-of-trade-levy-pain-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
